headline.print_headline: Malta Stun Wasteful Bulgarians in Sofia Draw
headline.main: Malta Stun Wasteful Bulgarians in Sofia Draw

lead_paragraph: Minnows Malta, who had failed to score in their previous six matches, stunned Bulgaria with a second-half penalty by Clayton Failla to draw 1-1 in their Euro 2016 Group H qualifier on Sunday.
